               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa  gǝnzät “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-117vb)&#xD;
- Introduction (fols. 3ra-4vb), incomplete.&#xD;
- Discourse of St. Athanasius on death (fols. 12rb-16ra)&#xD;
- Mäṣḥaf zä-wäḍʾat ʾǝm-ʾIyärusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 20ra-26vb)&#xD;
- Antiphons (kǝśtät, ʾaryam, mäzmur) (fols. 33vb-34va, 50rb-51ra, 81va-vb, 83ra-84ra, 88rb-vb, 90ra, 91va-92ra, 94va-vb, 98ra-rb)&#xD;
- Homily by St. Jacob of Sarug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols. 53vb-55va)&#xD;
- Lǝfafä ṣǝdq “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols. 69ra-71va)&#xD;
- Mängädä sämay “Journey to Heaven” (fols. 71va-73rb)&#xD;
- Homily by ʾabba Sälama, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 77va-79vb)&#xD;
- Maṣḥafa  ʾardǝʾǝt “Book of Disciples” (fols. 115va-117vb, 1ra-vb)&#xD;
&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
